These scripts are used to run rpmlint and shellcheck on spec files and shell scripts under the jalop directory.

The rpmlint/shellcheck program must be installed on your system in order to run these scripts.

To install rpmlint: yum install rpmlint
To install shellcheck: yum install ShellCheck
To install python-magic: pip3 install python-magic

To run them, from this directory:
python3 run_rpmlint.py
python3 run_shellcheck.py


The script checksec_builds.sh is used to validate whether rpath is present in built artifacts.
It validates libraries installed to the system and locally built artifacts.

To run it, from this directory:
bash checksec_builds.sh
